Package keystore_tutorial

Class DelegatingKeyStoreSpi

java.lang.Object
java.security.KeyStoreSpi
keystore_tutorial.DelegatingKeyStoreSpi
Direct Known Subclasses:
ReloadingKeyStoreFileSpi, ReloadingPemFileKeyStoreSpi
public abstract class DelegatingKeyStoreSpi extends KeyStoreSpi
Implements KeyStoreSpi by delegating SPI calls to an instance of KeyStore. The delegate keystore can be replaced on demand when the underlying certificate(s) and key(s) require that. The class returns aliases in sorted order instead of the order that underlying KeyStore would return them. This allows user to have expected fallback behavior when KeyManager selects server certificate in cases when SNI is not set or unknown SNI servername is requested
